{"tid":1156740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】帶埋阿媽去拍拖 失婚何艷娟同200億身家男友打得火熱","createTime":"2019-05-15T20:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T03:35:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f1971d66fafea2bcc4f09cd2900fac0a0f0c9117","tid":1156740,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T20:45:39.000Z","msg":"27歲失婚港姐何艷娟孔雀開屏，5月初才宣佈回復單身，跟坐擁30億身家的澳博營運總裁吳志誠閃離，結束了「壽命」不足1年的爺孫戀婚姻，一個華麗轉身，何艷娟被爆戀上已故教育家陳樹渠的長子陳燿璋，其家族資產逾200億，身家比何艷娟前夫更上一層樓，兩人打得火熱，母親節前夕拍拖遊覽蒲台島，何艷娟更帶埋媽咪食海鮮，被讀者吳小姐透過「爆相爆片」分享。<br />\n吳小姐接受電話訪問表示，上周六（11日）下午約2時許，在蒲台島的海鮮酒家內見到兩人，她說：「佢哋啱啱落船，何艷娟兩母女同男朋友一齊，佢同媽咪好似樣，但好似好驚俾人認到，佢哋坐喺酒家裏面，再等埋男友嘅外國朋友嚟食飯，之後男友叫埋佢一齊去揀海鮮，個女仔表現得好姣好嗲。」<br />\n從吳小姐提供的相片所見，着背心裙襯草帽的何艷娟打扮淑女，估唔到她拍拖都帶埋媽咪同行，由於翌日就是母親節，相信陳燿璋是跟伯母食飯預祝，但同枱又有幾位他的外籍友人，這個組合就變得很奇怪，可能陳燿璋是超級大忙人，將拍拖、母親節、朋友飯局三合一，節省時間一舉三得？而現年55歲的陳燿璋，跟何艷娟媽咪年齡相近，大家有傾有講好融洽。<br />\n何艷娟和媽咪母女情深，兩人不時結伴行街，前年母親節，何艷娟在社交網晒合照並留言：「母親節快樂！小時候在寄宿學校讀書，後來又去了英國，以前常常擔心能陪家人的時間太少了。真的非常感恩現在的我長大了能夠天天陪在媽媽身邊，陪她逛街、看電影、吃東西、聊天，感覺很幸福充實。謝謝你把我養得這麼健康這麼白。我一定會用我的一生好好報答你。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557829630_3420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557829630_3420.jpg&h=a0429b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557829630_552d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557829630_552d.jpg&h=7659c736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557830298_e653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557830298_e653.jpg&h=86c79f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190516/59600521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190516%2F59600521&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2AqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=1f349e50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190516%2F59600521&h=83beb004\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190516/59600521</a>"},{"pid":"52237d159349c6ec5877d2e89ce74bc2fb698dea","tid":1156740,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:09:06.000Z","msg":"who??"},{"pid":"f739a9281c97369e5afcf194524d5841acb974d1","tid":1156740,"uid":62850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:11:20.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"72a18185a461f1ef2ff7fc3d363f05b8023c1c45","tid":1156740,"uid":189528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"等睇下一個傻仔被分身家"},{"pid":"54716dd3c4071057274413bfbae1292565e8715e","tid":1156740,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a18185a461f1ef2ff7fc3d363f05b8023c1c45","tid":1156740,"uid":189528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"等睇下一個傻仔被分身家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac52541514a6dd80b6217c401e027d3c24a6c8ee","tid":1156740,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54716dd3c4071057274413bfbae1292565e8715e","tid":1156740,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a18185a461f1ef2ff7fc3d363f05b8023c1c45","tid":1156740,"uid":189528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"等睇下一個傻仔被分身家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T01:34:40.000Z","msg":"On9呢家野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"